snippet.title: Demonschool first trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1900250/Demonschool/

Demonschool is a new-style tactics RPG, with an involved story, many characters to befriend, and many demons to smite. 

more info: www.demonschool.com
